name: THIS IS EYEBALL COUNTRY
description: I created this piece early in 2020 for a CREEPY GALS prompt hosted by Lifeform Podcast. I attempted to create a cinematic scene using my own characters and I was heavily influenced by two of my favorite films, "Pulp Fiction" and "Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas". This was originally drawn with pen on paper and then later finalized with color and collage elements in Photoshop. This is a TOMORROWMAN original artwork.
